Class VMConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • server.XMLReader.VMConfig

  • public class VMConfig
extends java.lang.Object
    This class holds the info for a VM that is running on a PM. E.g. its type and RAM size This is the info specified in the XML file, from it we will create VMInfo objects
